📣 BIG ANNOUNCEMENT 📣 The 𝗕𝗲 𝗬𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗢𝘄𝗻 𝗖𝗵𝗲𝗲𝗿𝗹𝗲𝗮𝗱𝗲𝗿 𝗣𝗲𝗽 𝗥𝗮𝗹𝗹𝘆 𝗝𝗼𝘂𝗿𝗻𝗮𝗹™ is here! 

Friends, do you want 2023 to be the best year of your life? (Of course you do 🙋‍♀️) Then this journal is for you, it’s packed with weekly Pep Talks, Daily Affirmations, and lots of enthusiasm to help keep you inspired, motivated and encouraged in your daily life! 

BUY IT NOW! Go to my website, link in bio and shipping starts on 1/11/22. Get ready. Get excited. It is happening. 𝗥𝗘𝗔𝗗𝗬? 𝗢𝗞! 🙌

📣ENTHUSIASM 📣 Friends! I’m excited to help you create the very best year of your entire life! Ready? Ok!

Our Choreographed Routine:

1) 𝗬𝗼𝘂 get the 𝗕𝗲 𝗬𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗢𝘄𝗻 𝗖𝗵𝗲𝗲𝗿𝗹𝗲𝗮𝗱𝗲𝗿 𝗣𝗲𝗽 𝗥𝗮𝗹𝗹𝘆 𝗝𝗼𝘂𝗿𝗻𝗮𝗹™ 
2) 𝗬𝗼𝘂 feel motivated with weekly Pep Talks
3) 𝗬𝗼𝘂 feel inspired with daily affirmations 
4) 𝗬𝗼𝘂 feel encouraged by writing yourself 𝙮𝙤𝙪𝙧𝙨𝙚𝙡𝙛 a daily Pep Talk. After all, no one has your back like 𝙮𝙤𝙪 do. 𝙔𝙤𝙪 are where the magic happens!

🚀 Link in bio. It’s happening. Let’s do this! #cantstopwontstop

📣AND 5, 6, 7, 8! 📣 It’s me, hi, I’m your Cheerleader Christine. Friends, I’m excited to see so many new faces, welcome to the Pep Rally. Let’s reintroduce ourselves, I’ll go first! Ready? Ok! 🙋‍♀️

I am a Motivational Speaker and Women’s Corporate Instructor, with experience in executing programs that support gender justice and personal growth. ✨I am dedicated to encouraging women to invest in themselves and have combined my 20 years of media & marketing experience, including 13 years at O, The Oprah Magazine with clients like Amazon, Target, and Unilever, to create the Be Your OWN Cheerleadertraining platform! 👌

My enthusiasm is at an all time high when I’m facilitating our most popular program, The Build The Best You Masterclass Series. A “Pep Rally style” Women’s Personal Growth program designed to help organizations support, motivate, and close the allyship gap with the women in their workplace. (This is what I live for. This is where I thrive. I’m sitting in my pink blazer, drafting new coursework as we speak!) 📝💕

Wait, the fun doesn’t stop there! If your company doesn’t offer the Build The Best You program (yet!) I will bring the encouragement and enthusiasm to your home (and by home, I mean your phone!)📲💥Join the Pep Rally Membership starting in July to receive online workshops, daily affirmations, pep talks and more!

And when I’m not working, you can find me with a diet coke in hand, getting a big hair blow out, posting Pep Talks and trying to sneak in #proudmom pictures of my 11-year-old son James. That is until he sees it, dies of embarrassment, and forces me to remove it. Can’t blame a girl for trying! 👩‍👦

But friends, in all seriousness, this is your reminder to get excited about your life again! I’m here to help you do it, you’ve got a personal cheerleader to help you every step of the way. Let’s do this!#cantstopwontstop 💥💃
